	(646,2,'2009-10-27 18:11:03','2009-10-27 16:11:03','<a href=\"https://myspace.com/swingweekender\"><img class=\"alignleft\" src=\"http://c1.ac-images.myspacecdn.com/images02/78/l_fe325d13732e4cc5b7cdc32ee3f16940.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"167\" height=\"237\" /></a> Anfang Dezember ist es wieder soweit: <strong>Swingweekender</strong> in Leipzig.\r\n\r\nDas heisst zwei Nächte lang im Stile der Swinging 20er, voll gepackt mit Aufführungen, Workshops, Film, live Musik, DJs und natürlich viel Spaß, Party &amp; Tanz bis früh in den Morgen..\r\n\r\nTickets für das Wochenende gibts für nur 20.00 EUR bei <a href=\"http://www.culton.de/\">Culton hier</a>\r\n\r\nMehr infos hier: <a href=\"https://myspace.com/swingweekender\">swingweekender Leipzig</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Das Programm:</strong>\r\n<strong>Freitag</strong>\r\n20:00 Jive Workshop with the Jukebox Stompers\r\n21:15 Burlesque with Miss Mama Ulita\r\n21:30 Andrej Hermlin &amp; his Band (GER)\r\n23:00 Laura B &amp; the Moonlighters (UK)\r\n00:00 Record Hop with Turky (F) &amp; Miss Aloha (UK)\r\n05:00 The dance shoes go sleeping\r\n05:15 The Hepcats as well !!!\r\n\r\n<strong>Samstag:</strong>\r\n14:45 Open the eyes,shake your legs,stretch your arms-The second day begins!\r\n15:00 Swing Movies\r\n15:15 Hair Workshop with Salon Kitty\r\n15:30 Swing Market\r\n17:00 Lecture with Swanee &amp; Wuthe: Funny little stories behind the scene of Swing history\r\n19:00 Showdancing with Swing in L.E. &amp; Jukebox Stompers &amp; Swing Connection\r\n20:00 Swing Dance Workshop\r\n21:15 BurlesqueShow with Little Miss Bodacious\r\n21:30 The Ballroom Kings (IT)\r\n23:00 The Extraordinaires (UK)\r\n00:00 Record Hop with the German Dream Team: Miss SwinginSwanee, Schellak Wuthe &amp; Kaiser L\r\n06:00 Enough is enough - we go sleeping\r\n\r\n<strong>Sonntag</strong>\r\n11:00 Breakfast for all Hepcats','Swing it Again - Swingweekender Leipzig 2009',0,'','publish','open','open','','swing-it-again-swingweekender-leipzig-2009','','','2018-01-18