	(3156,2,'2011-09-07 13:07:07','2011-09-07 12:07:07','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3164\" title=\"Screen shot 2011-08-31 at 14.11.20\" src=\"http://www.hopit.de/files/2011/08/Screen-shot-2011-08-31-at-14.11.20.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"602\" height=\"139\" /></p>\r\nKleiner, feiner Workshop Tipp:\r\n\r\nDaniel Ludevig hält einen Lindy-hop/Swing/Charleston Workshop nächsten Mittwoch (14. September) von 19:45-22:15\r\nBrandenburgische Str. 46 in Wilmersdorf;\r\n\r\n<em>Workshop description: We will continue with lindy-hop and swing basics, feeling, musicality, tandem Charleston and jumps. Comfort with basic swing is required but the rest will be taught. If you love the feeling of finding freedom and energy in your dance, this is the course for you! </em>\r\n\r\nThe course will be 2.5 hours long and cost 30€/person.\r\n\r\nLocation: We will continue our lessons in our new space at Mittenwalder Strasse 15. Ring \"Mittenwalder Studio\" then walk through to the 3rd door on the left and then up 1-flight of stairs and the studio will be right in front of you.\r\n\r\nAnmeldung per Email an: dludevig@gmail.com\r\n\r\nhttp://www.dancingwithmanagement.com','Berlin: Lindy Hop, Swing, Charleston Workshop mit Daniel Ludevig',0,'','publish','open','open','','berlin-lindy-hop-swing-charleston-workshop-mit-daniel-ludevig','','','2011-09-05 12:48:14','2011-09-05 11:48:14','',0,'http://www.hopit.de/?p=3156',0,'post','',0),
