	(4917,2,'2014-11-30 16:40:57','2014-11-30 15:40:57','<img src=\"http://www.hopit.de/files/2014/11/how-to-win.jpg\" alt=\"how-to-win\" width=\"1754\" height=\"1022\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4918\" />\r\n\r\nIch hab kürzlich einen Vortrag gegeben über: `How to win a Dance Battle`. Hier die Slides und meine Recherche Notes. Viel Spaß und Erfolg aufm Dancefloor ;)\r\n\r\n<iframe src=\"//www.slideshare.net/slideshow/embed_code/42183006\" width=\"476\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\r\n\r\n<strong>How To Win Dance Battle</strong>\r\nDid I ever won a dance battle ? - Disclamer: I never did\r\nDid I ever took part  at a dance battle ? - Disclamer: I never did\r\n\r\nBUT:  I\'m dancing swing for the last 6 years, used to to a masterclass 2 years ago, got asked for an follow up, today I\'ll give you tips for everyday situation.\r\n\r\n<strong>What\'s a dance battle? </strong>\r\nBattle = Dance oOff / Jam, History, Break Dance, Street Dance, Capoeira dance, Swing Dance\r\n\r\n<strong>How to recognize you\'r in a dance battle:</strong>\r\nRules, dance floor, dance circle, multiple rounds\r\n\r\n<strong>Moves, Attitude:</strong>\r\n<strong>DO:</strong> Music, Shine, Respect, Personality, Fun, Rhythm, hit the beats, take your time, Look at the opponent, steal and mimic moves, watch ur opponent, be Cool, be creative, improvise, get ur personal step, Cloth Style. \r\n3Steps: impressive start, solid moves, fancy ending\r\n\r\n<strong>DONTS:</strong>\r\nDon\'t take your shirt of, Pointy Fingers, Animal Moves, Hit, punch: http://www.break.com/video/winning-a-dance-battle-with-one-punch-2191470, be aggressive, interfere you opponent, High Heels, Pole\r\n\r\n<strong>Moves:</strong>\r\nrock steps, side step, kicks, freeze, slides, leans, slowmotion, spin, wave, head stand, head spin, backflip, somersault, moon walk, down on the floor, itching, robot (botting) Robo Mad chadd: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_nXMGDcIEbs, roboboys poppin john http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ngUOX2J7AZA\r\nAlphabetic jazz: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pbteWH-3QlY\r\nInsane robo dance: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4YJ3BTKMILw\r\n\r\n<strong>Examples:</strong>\r\nNola girl jam 2013: http://www.nolagirljam.com/\r\nold school battle: http://www.hopit.de/2013/09/stockholm-oldschool-battle, http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e-wx4DqmpxU&list=PLF8B76DEB9F1AE4DE#t=64\r\nBerlin dance battle: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5ZsZQ-zyi-I\r\n\r\n<strong>Sources:</strong>\r\n6yr gel BGRL Terra: http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-504784_162-57572367-10391705/you-need-to-see-this-6-year-old-girl-perform-at-a-dance-battle/\r\nhttp://topsecret.ning.com\r\nhttp://www.howcast.com/videos/511761-How-to-Win-a-Turfing-Battle-Street-Dance\r\nhow to win a dance off: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_PouqhRIoAg\r\nindian how to dance battle: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-6DWg1v2qdM\r\nhttp://www.wikihow.com/Win-the-Make-Your-Mark-Shake-It-Up-Dance-Off\r\nkid vs. adult dance:  lil boy https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_detailpage&v=4Wl-uSwHufk#t=160\r\nAmazing how to dance: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S0yuk45LbeU\r\nPulp Fiction - Jack Rabbit Slims Twist Contest (Chuck Berry - You Never Can Tell) http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-dt6nHTKnbs -> Fun fact: they never won, but stole the trophy\r\nEmergency guide men: http://www.videojug.com/film/dance-moves-an-emergency-guide-for-men\r\n','How to win a Dance Battle',0,'','publish','open','open','','how-to-win-a-dance-battle','','','2014-11-30 16:40:57','2014-11-30 15:40:57','',0,'http://www.hopit.de/?p=4917',0,'post','',0),
